    "content": "PLAKAR-PKG(1) General Commands Manual PLAKAR-PKG(1) NAME plakar-pkg — List installed Plakar plugins\nSYNOPSIS plakar pkg DESCRIPTION The plakar pkg lists the currently installed plugins.\nFILES ~/.cache/plakar/plugins/ Plugin cache directory. Respects XDG_CACHE_HOME if set. ~/.local/share/plakar/plugins Plugin directory. Respects XDG_DATA_HOME if set. SEE ALSO plakar-pkg-add(1), plakar-pkg-rm(1)\nPlakar July 11, 2025 PLAKAR-PKG(1)",
