    "content": "PLAKAR-PKG-RM(1) General Commands Manual PLAKAR-PKG-RM(1) NAME plakar-pkg-rm — Uninstall Plakar plugins\nSYNOPSIS plakar pkg rm plugin ... DESCRIPTION The plakar pkg rm command removes plugins that have been previously installed with plakar-pkg-add(1) command.\nThe list of plugins can be obtained with plakar-pkg(1).\nEXAMPLES Removing a plugin:\n$ plakar pkg epic-v1.2.3 $ plakar pkg rm epic-v1.2.3 SEE ALSO plakar-pkg(1), plakar-pkg-add(1)\nPlakar July 11, 2025 PLAKAR-PKG-RM(1)",
