    "content": "PLAKAR-AGENT(1) - General Commands Manual\nNAME plakar agent - Run the Plakar agent\nSYNOPSIS plakar agent [-foreground] [-log filename] [stop]\nDESCRIPTION The plakar agent command starts the Plakar agent which will execute subsequent plakar(1) commands on their behalfs for faster processing. plakar agent continues running indefinitely.\nThe options are as follows:\n-foreground\nDo not daemonize agent, run in foreground.\n-log filename\nRedirect all output to filename.\nWith the stop argument, plakar agent will be stopped.\nDIAGNOSTICS The plakar agent utility exits 0 on success, and \u003e0 if an error occurs.\n0\nCommand completed successfully.\n\u003e0\nAn error occurred, such as invalid parameters, inability to create the repository, or configuration issues.\nSEE ALSO plakar(1)\nPlakar - February 1, 2025",
